[
  {
    "content_id": 340396,
    "reference_id": 24956,
    "title": "路得記 1:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>士師們從約書亞去世（約公元前1376年或1200年）到掃羅開始作王（約公元前1050年）。路得記記錄的事件發生在約公元前1100年。</p></li><li><p>以色列山地國中的饑荒通常是由乾旱引起的。</p></li><li><p>伯利恆是猶大北部山地的一個小鎮。</p></li><li><p>摩押，猶大東南的土地，有時在猶大沒有雨水的時候會有足夠的雨水。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:1",
          "end_ref": "08001001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340399,
    "reference_id": 24959,
    "title": "路得記1:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>以法他人屬於以法他族，他們聚集在猶大的伯利恆（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:19\">創35:19</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr4:4\">代上4:4</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:2",
          "end_ref": "08001002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340400,
    "reference_id": 24960,
    "title": "路得記1:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>基連娶了俄珥巴；瑪倫娶了路得（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:10\">4:10</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:4",
          "end_ref": "08001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340401,
    "reference_id": 24961,
    "title": "路得記1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>沒有丈夫，也沒有兒子（希伯來文字面意思<em>這女人一無所有了</em>）：拿俄米在情感上遭受了毀滅性的損失。她也沒有了經濟支持，失去繼承人使得她也喪失了對家庭未來的盼望。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:5",
          "end_ref": "08001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340402,
    "reference_id": 24962,
    "title": "路得記1:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>賜……與：同一個希伯來文動詞也出現在了<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:13\">4章13節</a>（「使她」〔enabled〕）。這兩處對神作為的提示把這個故事夾在了這兩個相似短語之間（文學上的首尾呼應<em>〔inclusio〕</em>）。神賜下美好的事物，比如糧食和孩子，而且神居於幕後看顧事物的普通運作過程。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08001006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:6",
          "end_ref": "08001006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340403,
    "reference_id": 24963,
    "title": "路得記1:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>他們可能只走了很短的距離，拿俄米就讓路得和俄珥巴回娘家了。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08001008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:8",
          "end_ref": "08001008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340404,
    "reference_id": 24964,
    "title": "路得記1:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>拿俄米在這裡給出了這卷書中幾個祝福中的第一個祝福。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08001009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:9",
          "end_ref": "08001009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340393,
    "reference_id": 24953,
    "title": "路得記1:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>路得捨不得拿俄米（有些英譯本譯為「路得緊緊抓住拿俄米」）：這裡使用的希伯來文動詞強調了路得對婆婆之愛的力量；這個詞與用來描述男人與妻子「連合」（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:24\">創2:24</a>）以及一個人對主忠心（專靠祂；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:4\">申4:4，</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:20\">10:20；</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:5\">書22:5</a>）的詞是同一個詞。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08001014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:14",
          "end_ref": "08001014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340394,
    "reference_id": 24954,
    "title": "路得記1:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>她所拜的神：每個國家的人都信仰自己本國的神。拿俄米認為路得會繼續敬拜摩押神。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08001015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:15",
          "end_ref": "08001015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340395,
    "reference_id": 24955,
    "title": "路得記1:16–17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001016-08001017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>路得奉耶和華的名起誓，這表明了她對以色列之神的堅定委身（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:11-Ruth2:12\">2:11–12</a>）和對拿俄米的忠誠。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08001016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:16",
          "end_ref": "08001017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340397,
    "reference_id": 24957,
    "title": "路得記1:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>希伯來文中的「神」（shadday）翻譯為全能者，體現出了神的大能和供應。拿俄米所訴之苦都是真的，但神卻恰恰供應了她所需要的一切（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:14-Ruth4:17\">4:14–17</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08001020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:20",
          "end_ref": "08001020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340398,
    "reference_id": 24958,
    "title": "路得記1:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08001022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>割大麥的時候是現在公曆的三月下旬到四月中旬之間。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08001022",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:22",
          "end_ref": "08001022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 1:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340410,
    "reference_id": 24970,
    "title": "路得記2:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>波阿斯是以利米勒的親屬，因此有資格成為兩位寡婦——路得和拿俄米的至親買贖者（見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"24971\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">2:20的研讀註釋</span>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08002001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:1",
          "end_ref": "08002001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 24971,
          "content_id": 340411,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "路得記2:20",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340413,
    "reference_id": 24973,
    "title": "路得記2:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在……身後拾取麥穗：收割麥子的人應該留下些麥穗供窮人拾取（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:9-Lev19:10\">利19:9–10，</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:22\">23:22；</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:19-Deut24:22\">申24:19–22</a>）。神供養窮人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08002002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:2",
          "end_ref": "08002002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340414,
    "reference_id": 24974,
    "title": "路得記2:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>她恰巧到了：路得似乎隨便選了一塊地去拾取麥穗；神通過日常生活中的選擇來看顧那些信靠祂的人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08002003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:3",
          "end_ref": "08002003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340415,
    "reference_id": 24975,
    "title": "路得記2:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>波阿斯認為路得是一位適婚的年輕女子（希伯來文為na‘arah）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08002005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:5",
          "end_ref": "08002005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340416,
    "reference_id": 24976,
    "title": "路得記2:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在屋子裡：以色列山區的許多農民會在田地旁搭棚子，以便在收割期使用。在漫長而辛苦的整日勞作中，工人會於午餐或其他間歇時用這些棚子來遮蔭。在某些山區仍然可以看到這樣的棚子。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08002007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:7",
          "end_ref": "08002007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340417,
    "reference_id": 24977,
    "title": "路得記2:8–9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002008-08002009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>波阿斯給了路得一項特權，讓她可以跟在年輕使女後面拾取麥穗。男人們割下麥子捆成小捆後，女人們收集這些小捆將其捆成大捆。摩西律法並不要求農夫允許拾穗者在麥捆運到打穀場之前就進入田地。</p></li><li><p>我已經吩咐僕人不可欺負你（有些英譯本譯為「我已經警告年輕人不要粗暴地對待你」）：波阿斯向路得保證，哪怕她在拾穗者應該進入田地之前就進去了，他的僕人也不會捉弄她或試圖將她趕出田地。</p></li><li><p>就可以喝……水：波阿斯的慷慨讓路得免於自己打水的辛勞。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08002008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:8",
          "end_ref": "08002009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340405,
    "reference_id": 24965,
    "title": "路得記2:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>你的一個使女（希伯來文字面意思<em>你的婢女</em>）：路得用的這個詞，將自己置於比波阿斯僕人更低的社會階層中。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08002013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:13",
          "end_ref": "08002013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340406,
    "reference_id": 24966,
    "title": "路得記2:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>波阿斯分享食物給路德，這樣的款待遠遠超過了他的責任範圍。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08002014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:14",
          "end_ref": "08002014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340407,
    "reference_id": 24967,
    "title": "路得記2:15–16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002015-08002016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>午飯後波阿斯給收麥僕人的吩咐，使得路得能夠更加有效地多拾麥穗。波阿斯為路得提供的幫助，遠遠超過了拾穗律法的要求。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08002015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:15",
          "end_ref": "08002016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340408,
    "reference_id": 24968,
    "title": "路得記2:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>路得將剩下的烘了的穗子帶給拿俄米，這體現出了她對婆婆的用心以及她的慷慨。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08002018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:18",
          "end_ref": "08002018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340409,
    "reference_id": 24969,
    "title": "路得記2:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>麥穗（有些英譯本譯為「這些麥穗」）：在一般情況下，路得不可能拾取到接近一伊法的大麥（約三分之二蒲式耳）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08002019",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:19",
          "end_ref": "08002019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340411,
    "reference_id": 24971,
    "title": "路得記2:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>至親買贖者（family redeemer，和合本譯為「至近的親屬」，希伯來文為go’el）：律法規定至親買贖者，即最近的男性親屬，應該幫助陷入經濟困難的親屬（見「<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"203149\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotesThemes\">至親買贖者</span>」主題註釋；另見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"19448\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">利25:25的研讀註釋</span>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08002020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:20",
          "end_ref": "08002020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 19448,
          "content_id": 759158,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "利未記 25:25",
          "language": "zht"
        },
        {
          "reference_id": 203149,
          "content_id": 700212,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotesThemes",
          "label": "至親買贖者",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340412,
    "reference_id": 24972,
    "title": "路得記2:21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08002021",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>作者有五次提到路得時（措辭上）說她是「摩押女子路得」（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:22\">1:22，</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:2\">2:2</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:21\">21，</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:5\">4:5</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:10\">10</a>），反覆提醒我們路得並非以色列人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08002021",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:21",
          "end_ref": "08002021",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 2:21"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340422,
    "reference_id": 24982,
    "title": "路得記3:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>安身之處：<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:9\">1章9節</a>中拿俄米為路得和俄珥巴禱告時，用了一個與這個詞相關的詞。現在她提出了一個可能會鼓勵波阿斯為了路得採取行動的方案。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 3:1",
          "end_ref": "08003001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 3:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340423,
    "reference_id": 24983,
    "title": "路得記3:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "08003002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>作為至親，波阿斯可以成為路得和拿俄米的至親買贖者（見研讀註釋<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"24971\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">2:20，</span><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"24988\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">3:9</span>）。</p></li><li><p>打穀場是一塊平坦的石頭或硬化的土地。農夫將麥捆鋪在其上，敲打麥捆讓麥粒與秸稈分離。然後農夫會用木叉或鏟子將帶著穀粒的秸稈拋向空中簸揚。微風會把較輕的秸稈和<span>糠皮</span>吹到下風處，而較重的穀粒則落在了場上。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "08003002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "RUT 3:2",
          "end_ref": "08003002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "RUT 3:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
